        "timestamp": "2023-02-26 15:07:57.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHere is the latest performance report with this change:\n\n#############################################################################\n##             P E R F O R M A N C E   T E S T   R E S U L T S             ##\n#############################################################################\n 2.Delete 5 children                        limit    300 took     226 ms PASS\n 3.Batch delete 100 children                limit    250 took     211 ms PASS\n 4.Delete 50 grandchildren                  limit    300 took     223 ms PASS\n 5.Batch delete 500 grandchildren           limit    125 took     131 ms FAIL\n 7.Delete 5 whole lists                     limit  1,300 took   1,250 ms PASS\n 8.Batch delete 100 whole lists             limit    250 took     215 ms PASS\n 9.Delete 10 lists elements                 limit    600 took     545 ms PASS\n10.Batch delete 500 lists elements          limit     60 took      51 ms PASS",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
